\section{Profile}
\small{
Physics teacher with strong foundations in software development and analytical problem solving. Experience delivering projects across the full software development lifecycle including design, implementation, integration, testing and documentation. Proficient in Python and C++ with exposure to structured data formats (JSON, XML) and SQL fundamentals. Interested in telecommunications systems and 5G technologies, and motivated to contribute to high-value Software R\&D in a collaborative engineering environment.
}

\section{Technical Skills}
\small{
\textbf{Programming:} Python, C++, MATLAB (familiar with C\# and .NET concepts) \\
\textbf{Software Engineering:} Object-oriented programming, SDLC, modular design, integration and validation testing, debugging \\
\textbf{Data \& Technologies:} JSON, XML, SQL basics, NumPy, Pandas, Matplotlib \\
\textbf{Systems:} Linux and Windows OS, networking fundamentals, communication protocol concepts \\
\textbf{Tools:} Git, Visual Studio Code, structured documentation and version control \\
\textbf{Core Competencies:} Technical problem solving, teamwork, adaptability, clear communication
}

